    "body": "The static CampaignProgress doesn't feel like a good fit.  See #7213 for some earlier discussion about recording our campaign progression.  I still think that the most flexible way to implement this will be via a Lua API for saving arbitrary data, which then lets us implement mission-objective specific progression (e.g. the C&C commando mission, which branched based on which structure you destroyed), and persisting information such as base layout across missions.\n"
  },
